OL,7,FMinisters and water companies would
OL,8,Fbe legally obliged to end the dumping
OL,9,Fof sewage in Britain's waterways
OL,10,Funder new legislation proposed by
OL,11,FLabour, the party has said.
OL,13,FShadow environment secretary Jim
OL,14,FMcMahon said Labour would put forward
OL,15,Fa new Bill which would make it a
OL,16,Flegal requirement to monitor all
OL,17,Fsewage outlets. The proposed
OL,18,Flegislation would also create a
OL,19,Fstatutory underpinning for penalties
OL,20,Fover failures to adhere.
OL,3,CLabour pledges to introduce measures
OL,4,Cto end sewage dumping in Britain's
OL,5,Cwaterways
